### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Login (Run this first to get token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Get Cart (requires login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Add Product to Cart (requires login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "productId": "YOUR_PRODUCT_ID",
  "quantity": 2
}

### 4. Update Cart Item (requires login)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/YOUR_CART_ITEM_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### 5. Remove Item from Cart (requires login)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items/YOUR_CART_ITEM_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Clear Cart (requires login)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}